01CDFBEB.Line47.6DE47: I’m going to help you. I know the Horadrim’s ways. Your magic. Even that coded writing system you use.

204583FF.Line51.7FA05: That's a good speech. Might even convince the man you should be telling it to. Come on. I'm headed to him.

542E7703.Line55.7FA05: It was, once. Now? I suppose time will tell.

7B97AD88.Line35.6DE47: She’s brilliant. One of my favorites.

9BC2756D.Line49.6DE47: And don't tell me it’s too dangerous. Lilith took my mother, I’ll do whatever it takes to stop her.

BA26DDC8.Line53.6DE47: But you're Horadrim. Isn’t this your vault?

CDE508E7.Line43.6DE47: Have you read her treatises? Never mind--you can tell me on the road.

FB3FFC35.MenuLabel: “Neyrelle. What have you been up to?”
